data.description: HERE IS YOUR RARE FIND! Come home to this BEAUTIFULLY updated, cozy CRAFTSMAN style home on 5+ usable acres with a small yr-round CREEK. From the moment you step inside, you'll feel AT HOME! Each room has been updated, while keeping the charm intact, but every bit functional. On the main floor are 2 bdrms, 2 full baths, an open-plan living & dining area that provides room for gatherings. Kitchen boasts white Shaker cabinets and NEW Samsung appliances & an island. Laundry rm/full bath off mud room. Upstairs, are two LARGE bdrms and a spacious loft/office area. Enjoy the view of morning sunrises & MT. RAINIER from the wrap-around COVERED PORCH. Outside, is a 1 car garage, garden space, greenhouse, canning shed, firepit & tons of fruit trees.
